main event: Two oval-shaped objects were observed by two civilian women near the moon.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for approximately 14-20 minutes., The objects were seen flying in formation., The color of the objects was described as luminous., The observers were civilians with previous experience in air observation., The objects displayed maneuvering behavior that exceeded that of known aircraft.
witness description: civilian women, one being the wife of a DC-3 pilot
